## Environment Variables

# Set to where you want the config files stored
APP_DIR=/mnt/data/apps

# Set to where you want your media files stored
MEDIA_DIR=/mnt/data/media/

# Set to where you keep your downloads
# Movies/TV will be moved from this folder
DOWNLOAD_DIR=/mnt/data/downloads

# Set to the hostname you want to use for your media services
# e.g. home.amer.dev  is my hostname
# This will create:
# plex.home.amer.dev
# tv.home.amer.dev
# movies.home.amer.dev
# etc. etc.
WEB_DOMAIN="home.amer.dev"

# Set the nginx address to the static IP of the server you are running this one
NGINX_ADDRESS=10.100.20.41


